channel.description: I know this is a weird topic may be spam idk but you can't have a username with java in it. Like Your name can't be like Java Man2332 or something.

item.title: Java names
item.dc:creator: @usama299 usama299
item.description:
@usama299 wrote:

[quote=“CoonHunter, post:10, topic:392595”][quote author=Phaze One link=topic=489767.msg3582694#msg3582694 date=1303921620]

I know this is a weird topic may be spam idk but you can’t have a username with java in it. Like Your name can’t be like Java Man2332 or something.

It’s because having the name Java injects codein the server and allows you access to admin commands.

Are you trolling or
[/quote]
He is trolling, and showing the real effect it could have (as in none) within the same troll. It was a retarded move to be blocked.[/quote]
